The #1 Station for Podcasts & Entertainment! To be in the know is to have the plug, which means staying on TRACC.
Detailed description -Dj Chic Chick Presents.... TRACC RADIO the podcast station that is the plug to informative interviews and untold stories with your some of favorite entertainers in music, film and television. Tune in to hear comedy inserts and skits produced by Tina Redmond aka Dj Chic Chick as she cut up with some of your favorite comedians. Also follow her journey to places that will become your favorite hotspots for pop up events, travelers, foodies, shoppers and tourism across the world.
